---
---

<section class="section anti-gaspi" id="anti-gaspi">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="anti-gaspi-inner" data-animate>
      <div class="anti-gaspi-content">
        <div class="badge badge-green">Mission anti-gaspi</div>
        <h2>Rien ne se perd,<br />tout se cuisine.</h2>
        <p>
          En France, chaque foyer jette en moyenne 30 kg d'aliments par an.
          DisChef est ne pour changer ca.
        </p>
        <ul class="anti-gaspi-list">
          <li>
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>Le Chef priorise les ingredients qui vont perimer</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>Des recettes adaptees a ce que vous avez, pas a ce que vous n'avez pas</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>Un planning qui optimise chaque achat de la semaine</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>Suivi de votre gaspillage sauve</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#download" class="btn btn-primary">
          Rejoindre le mouvement
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="anti-gaspi-visual">
        <div class="anti-gaspi-card">
          <div class="agc-icon">♻️</div>
          <div class="agc-stat">
            <span class="agc-number">30 kg</span>
            <span class="agc-label">de nourriture gaspillee par foyer / an</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="anti-gaspi-card agc-highlight">
          <div class="agc-icon">🧑‍🍳</div>
          <div class="agc-stat">
            <span class="agc-number">Le Chef</span>
            <span class="agc-label">analyse votre frigo et sauve ce qui peut l'etre</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .anti-gaspi {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--slate-50) 0%, #ffffff 100%);
  }

  .anti-gaspi-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .anti-gaspi-inner {
      flex-direction: row;
      gap: 80px;
    }
  }

  .anti-gaspi-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .anti-gaspi-content h2 {
    margin-top: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .anti-gaspi-content > p {
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .anti-gaspi-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .anti-gaspi-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--slate-700);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .check {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    background: #ecfdf5;
    color: #059669;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .anti-gaspi-visual {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 360px;
  }

  .anti-gaspi-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid var(--slate-200);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 24px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .anti-gaspi-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .agc-highlight {
    border-color: var(--frigo-200);
    background: var(--frigo-50);
  }

  .agc-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .agc-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .agc-number {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--slate-900);
  }

  .agc-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--slate-500);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
</style>
